description: Deletes a batch of evaluation jobs. An evaluation job can only be deleted if it has following status FAILED, COMPLETED, and STOPPED. You can request up to 25 model evaluation jobs be deleted in a single request.

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: A JSON object containing the HTTP status codes and the ARNs of evaluation jobs that failed to be deleted.

nested_items.name: jobIdentifier
nested_items.description: The ARN of the evaluation job being deleted.

nested_items.name: code
nested_items.description: A HTTP status code of the evaluation job being deleted.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: A status message about the evaluation job deletion.

nested_items.name: evaluationJobs
nested_items.description: The list of evaluation jobs for deletion.

nested_items.name: jobIdentifier
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the evaluation job for deletion.

nested_items.name: jobStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the evaluation job for deletion.
